# How to submit a Signal Proposal?

## What is a Signal Proposal

This is used as the name says, to send signals to the DAO. Something like a rule for the DAO can be immortalized in the blockchain by use of a signal dao. Or any other sort of non bank business but the DAO would like locked into the blockchain.

## Instructions

### From the DAO overview page

* Click "View Proposals" button

![](https://i.imgur.com/970wufr.png)

### From the Proposals Page

* Click the "New Poposal" button

![](https://i.imgur.com/br5yY1q.png)

### From the New Proposal Page

* Click the " Signal" button

![](https://i.imgur.com/nv6SIST.png)


### From the popup window

* Fill out what you would like to name the proposal in the "Title" Field
* If you have a link to support the proposal enter it in the "Link" field
* Enter the argument you would like for this proposal to be passed by the DAO in the "descritpion" field.
* Click "Submit" 
 
![](https://i.imgur.com/mgSb31h.png)

If you made any mistakes, the option to fix them is now :)

![](https://i.imgur.com/u3mUfKt.png)

and then hit submit after you fix any errors

### Confirm the Transaction in metamask

![](https://i.imgur.com/7PXT5AA.png)

